T02D1638:267a-0: @267a * // rigs lnga mkha' 'gro'i bstod pa bzhugs /
T02D1638:267a-2: * // aom rje btsun he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1638:267a-3: thabs dang shes rab bdag nyid can //
T02D1638:267a-4: thugs rjes skur sprul 'gro don mdzad //
T02D1638:267a-5: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang phyug gtso //
T02D1638:267a-6: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D1638:267a-7: zhal bzhi phyag bzhi spyan gsum mdzes //
T02D1638:267a-8: zhabs gnyis phyed krung gar tshul gyis //
T02D1638:267a-9: padma nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02D1638:267a-10: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes che //
T02D1638:267a-11: rdo rje dbyings ni mkhas chen po //
T02D1638:267a-12: rdo rje gsum mtshog dkyil 'khor gsum //
T02D1638:267a-14: rnam par snang mdzad rab tu dag / rdo rje zhi ba dga' ba che //
T02D1638:267a-15: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal mchog / rdo rje mkha' 'gro phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D1638:267a-16: rin chen rgyal po rab tu zab //
T02D1638:267a-17: rdo rje nam mkha' dri ma med //
T02D1638:267a-18: dngos gnyis dag pas gos pa med //
T02D1638:267a-21: rnam rtog nam mkha' rdo rje 'dzin //
T02D1638:267a-22: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pa brnyes //
T02D1638:267a-24: rdo rje dag pa gdon mi za //
T02D1638:267a-25: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa //
T02D1638:267a-26: sangs rgyas ngo bo nyid las byung //
